Class SparseDiscPhaseVar

  • java.lang.Object
    • jphase.AbstractDiscPhaseVar
      • jphase.SparseDiscPhaseVar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JMarkovElement, DiscPhaseVar, PhaseVar

    public class SparseDiscPhaseVar
extends AbstractDiscPhaseVar
    This class allows the creation and manipulation of Discrete Phase-type distributions represented by sparse (Flexible Compressed Row) matrices.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    German Riaño, Juan F. Perez
